title: Beautiful 2+1, Hardwood, New Kitchen, Stainless Steel, Garage
map_address: 231 West Olive Street near Eucalyptus / Manchester
posting_body: ['Beautiful and spacious 2+1 available.', ' Unit is located on the 2nd floor and has hardwood floors throughout.', ' Unit is very sunny, and the kitchen is brand new with new cabinets, new drawers, new quartz countertops, new vinyl, and new stainless-steel stove and fridge.', ' There is a dining area off of the living room, and both bedrooms have their own closets.', ' The bathroom is also spacious, and the unit comes with one assigned detached garage that fits one vehicle.', ' There are also blinds throughout, and a hallway closet for linens.', ' Property is only 15 units and is located in a cul-de-sac, off of Eucalyptus and Manchester.', " Complex has two laundry rooms and is close to Starbuck's, restaurants, banks, gym, and easy access to freeways.", ' Pets are okay, but NO smoking unit.', ' Landlords pay for water, trash, and landscaping.', ' Lease is for a one-year minimum.', ' Please call AFTER 9 a.m. and BEFORE 9 p.m., as this is a cell phone.']
